title: 'Made my friend really happy'
body: The long skirt is well-made and excellently designed. The stitching is good, and fabric design is exceptionally high quality for the product's price. The skirt flaring is just perfect making it delightfully compact for the normal use and elegantly playful during parties and while dancing. All in all, it is a wonderful product that brought smile to my friend's face.

title: 'Excellent quality for the price'
body: At this price, I was worried that the material would be flimsy, or the colour would be garish. Surprisingly, the material is reasonably good, and the colour is also pretty. I will probably get some elastic put into the waist band, as the belt area tends to get scrunched up when the knot is tied (it is okay for long kurtas, but doesn't work for cholis). All in all, definitely worth the money.
